        <content type="html" xml:base="https://emptyfridge.dev/ko/data_structure/tree/">&lt;p&gt;TreeлҠ” nodeмҷҖ edgeлЎң мқҙлЈЁм–ҙм§„ кі„мёөнҳ• мһҗлЈҢкө¬мЎ°лӢӨ. Graph кҙҖм җм—җм„ң ліҙл©ҙ &lt;strong&gt;connected
acyclic graph&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;, мҰү лӘЁл“  nodeк°Җ м—°кІ°лҗҳм–ҙ мһҲкі  cycleмқҙ м—ҶлҠ” graphлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;images&#x2F;DS&#x2F;Tree&#x2F;Treedatastructure.png&quot; alt=&quot;tree&quot; &#x2F;&gt;
source: &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.geeksforgeeks.org&#x2F;introduction-to-tree-data-structure-and-algorithm-tutorials&#x2F;&quot;&gt;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.geeksforgeeks.org&#x2F;introduction-to-tree-data-structure-and-algorithm-tutorials&#x2F;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;haegsim-seongjil&quot;&gt;н•өмӢ¬ м„ұм§Ҳ&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TreeлҘј мқҙн•ҙн•  л•Ң к°ҖмһҘ мӨ‘мҡ”н•ң м„ұм§ҲмқҖ м•„лһҳ м„ё к°Җм§ҖлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;nodeк°Җ &lt;code&gt;n&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;к°ңмқё treeлҠ” edgeк°Җ &lt;code&gt;n - 1&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;к°ңлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;мһ„мқҳмқҳ л‘җ node мӮ¬мқҙм—җлҠ” pathк°Җ м •нҷ•нһҲ н•ҳлӮҳл§Ң мЎҙмһ¬н•ңлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;edgeлҘј н•ҳлӮҳ м¶”к°Җн•ҳл©ҙ cycleмқҙ мғқкё°кі , edgeлҘј н•ҳлӮҳ м ңкұ°н•ҳл©ҙ м—°кІ°мқҙ лҒҠм–ҙм§„лӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ліҙнҶө н”„лЎңк·ёлһҳл°Қм—җм„ң л§җн•ҳлҠ” treeлҠ” rootк°Җ мһҲлҠ” &lt;strong&gt;rooted tree&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;лӢӨ. RootлҘј кё°мӨҖмңјлЎң
parent-child кҙҖкі„к°Җ мғқкё°кі , rootм—җм„ң л©Җм–ҙм§ҲмҲҳлЎқ depthк°Җ к№Ҡм–ҙм§„лӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;yongeo&quot;&gt;мҡ©м–ҙ&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;мҡ©м–ҙ&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;мқҳлҜё&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Root&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;л¶ҖлӘЁк°Җ м—ҶлҠ” мӢңмһ‘ node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Parent&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;м–ҙл–Ө node л°”лЎң мң„мқҳ node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Child&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;м–ҙл–Ө node л°”лЎң м•„лһҳмқҳ node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Sibling&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;к°ҷмқҖ parentлҘј кіөмң н•ҳлҠ” node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Leaf&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;childк°Җ м—ҶлҠ” node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Internal node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;leafк°Җ м•„лӢҢ node&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Degree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;child к°ңмҲҳ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Depth&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;rootм—җм„ң н•ҙлӢ№ nodeк№Ңм§Җ edge к°ңмҲҳ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Height&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;н•ҙлӢ№ nodeм—җм„ң к°ҖмһҘ лЁј leafк№Ңм§Җ edge к°ңмҲҳ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Subtree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;м–ҙл–Ө nodeлҘј rootлЎң н•ҳлҠ” л¶Җл¶„ tree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;мҳҲлҘј л“Өм–ҙ rootмқҳ depthлҠ” &lt;code&gt;0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙкі , leafмқҳ heightлҠ” &lt;code&gt;0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙлӢӨ. л¬ём ңл§ҲлӢӨ heightлҘј edge к°ңмҲҳ
лҢҖмӢ  node к°ңмҲҳлЎң м •мқҳн•ҳлҠ” кІҪмҡ°лҸ„ мһҲмңјлӢҲ л©ҙм ‘мқҙлӮҳ м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳ л¬ём ңм—җм„ңлҠ” м •мқҳлҘј лЁјм Җ нҷ•мқён•ҳлҠ”
кІҢ мўӢлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;tree-jongryu&quot;&gt;Tree мў…лҘҳ&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;binary-tree&quot;&gt;Binary Tree&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;к°Ғ nodeк°Җ мөңлҢҖ 2к°ңмқҳ childлҘј к°Җм§ҖлҠ” treeлӢӨ. ліҙнҶө childлҘј &lt;code&gt;left&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;right&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;лЎң л¶ҖлҘёлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;binary-search-tree&quot;&gt;Binary Search Tree&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Binary treeм—җ ordering ruleмқ„ м¶”к°Җн•ң treeлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #BFBDB6; background-color: #0D1017;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;plain&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;left subtreeмқҳ лӘЁл“  к°’ &amp;lt; root к°’ &amp;lt; right subtreeмқҳ лӘЁл“  к°’&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;мқҙ к·ңм№ҷ лҚ•л¶„м—җ search, insert, deleteк°Җ нҸүк· м ҒмңјлЎң &lt;code&gt;O(log n)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙ лҗ  мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ. н•ҳм§Җл§Ң treeк°Җ
н•ңмӘҪмңјлЎң кё°мҡёл©ҙ heightк°Җ &lt;code&gt;n&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙ лҗҳм–ҙ &lt;code&gt;O(n)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;к№Ңм§Җ лӮҳл№ м§„лӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;self-balancing-search-tree&quot;&gt;Self-balancing Search Tree&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Insert&#x2F;delete мқҙнӣ„ heightк°Җ л„Ҳл¬ҙ м»Өм§Җм§Җ м•ҠлҸ„лЎқ мҠӨмҠӨлЎң к· нҳ•мқ„ л§һм¶”лҠ” search treeлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AVL tree&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Red-black tree&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B-tree&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;м—¬кё°м„ң мЈјмқҳн•  м җмқҙ мһҲлӢӨ. &lt;strong&gt;B-treeлҠ” binary treeк°Җ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; н•ҳлӮҳмқҳ nodeк°Җ м—¬лҹ¬ keyмҷҖ м—¬лҹ¬ childлҘј
к°Җм§Ҳ мҲҳ мһҲлҠ” multi-way balanced search treeлӢӨ. Database indexлӮҳ filesystemм—җм„ң мһҗмЈј
л“ұмһҘн•ңлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;full-complete-perfect-binary-tree&quot;&gt;Full &#x2F; Complete &#x2F; Perfect Binary Tree&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;мқҙ м„ё мҡ©м–ҙлҠ” мқҙлҰ„мқҙ л№„мҠ·н•ҙм„ң мһҗмЈј н—·к°ҲлҰ°лӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;мў…лҘҳ&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;мЎ°кұҙ&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Full binary tree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;лӘЁл“  nodeмқҳ child к°ңмҲҳк°Җ 0к°ң лҳҗлҠ” 2к°ңлӢӨ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Complete binary tree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;л§Ҳм§Җл§ү levelмқ„ м ңмҷён•ң лӘЁл“  levelмқҙ кҪү м°Ё мһҲкі , л§Ҳм§Җл§ү levelмқҖ мҷјмӘҪл¶Җн„° мұ„мӣҢм ё мһҲлӢӨ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Perfect binary tree&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;лӘЁл“  internal nodeк°Җ child 2к°ңлҘј к°Җм§Җкі , лӘЁл“  leafк°Җ к°ҷмқҖ depthм—җ мһҲлӢӨ&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perfect binary treeлҠ” н•ӯмғҒ fullмқҙл©ҙм„ң completeлӢӨ. н•ҳм§Җл§Ң fullмқҙлқјкі  н•ҙм„ң completeмқё кІғмқҖ
м•„лӢҲкі , completeлқјкі  н•ҙм„ң fullмқё кІғлҸ„ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;traversal&quot;&gt;Traversal&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TraversalмқҖ treeмқҳ лӘЁл“  nodeлҘј н•ң лІҲм”© л°©л¬ён•ҳлҠ” л°©лІ•мқҙлӢӨ. Tree nodeк°Җ &lt;code&gt;n&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;к°ңлқјл©ҙ лӘЁл“ 
traversalмқҖ кё°ліём ҒмңјлЎң &lt;code&gt;O(n)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;images&#x2F;DS&#x2F;Tree&#x2F;full_binary_tree.png&quot; alt=&quot;Tree&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;dfs-depth-first-search&quot;&gt;DFS: Depth-First Search&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DFSлҠ” н•ң л°©н–ҘмңјлЎң лҒқк№Ңм§Җ лӮҙл Өк°”лӢӨк°Җ лӢӨмӢң лҸҢм•„мҳӨлҠ” л°©мӢқмқҙлӢӨ. Recursive call stackмқ„ м“°кұ°лӮҳ
м§Ғм ‘ stackмқ„ л§Ңл“Өм–ҙ кө¬нҳ„н•ңлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Binary treeм—җм„ң DFS мҲңнҡҢлҠ” rootлҘј м–ём ң л°©л¬ён•ҳлҠҗлғҗм—җ л”°лқј мқҙлҰ„мқҙ лӢ¬лқјм§„лӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;мҲңнҡҢ&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;мҲңм„ң&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;мҳҲмӢң&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Preorder&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Root -&amp;gt; Left -&amp;gt; Right&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;A-B-D-E-H-I-C-F-G&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Inorder&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Left -&amp;gt; Root -&amp;gt; Right&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;D-B-H-E-I-A-F-C-G&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Postorder&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Left -&amp;gt; Right -&amp;gt; Root&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;D-H-I-E-B-F-G-C-A&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;мҷёмҡ°лҠ” лІ•мқҖ к°„лӢЁн•ҳлӢӨ. LeftлҠ” н•ӯмғҒ RightліҙлӢӨ лЁјм Җ к°„лӢӨ. Rootк°Җ м•һмқҙл©ҙ preorder, мӨ‘к°„мқҙл©ҙ
inorder, л’Өл©ҙ postorderлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inorder traversalмқҖ binary search treeм—җм„ң нҠ№нһҲ мӨ‘мҡ”н•ҳлӢӨ. BSTлҘј inorderлЎң мҲңнҡҢн•ҳл©ҙ к°’мқҙ
м •л ¬лҗң мҲңм„ңлЎң лӮҳмҳЁлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #BFBDB6; background-color: #0D1017;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;rust&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF8F40;&quot;&gt;fn&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt; inorder&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(node&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt; Option&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt;Box&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt;TreeNode&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;, output&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;: &amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF8F40;&quot;&gt;mut&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt; Vec&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt;i32&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt;) {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF8F40;&quot;&gt;    if let&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #59C2FF;&quot;&gt; Some&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(node)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt; =&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; node {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt;        inorder&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(node&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;left&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt;as_ref&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(), output);&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        output&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt;push&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(node&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;val);&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt;        inorder&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(node&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;right&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F29668;&quot;&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB454;&quot;&gt;as_ref&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(), output);&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DFSмқҳ extra spaceлҠ” tree heightлҘј &lt;code&gt;h&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;лқјкі  н•  л•Ң recursive call stack кё°мӨҖ &lt;code&gt;O(h)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;лӢӨ.
Balanced treeлқјл©ҙ &lt;code&gt;O(log n)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, н•ңмӘҪмңјлЎң кё°мҡҙ treeлқјл©ҙ &lt;code&gt;O(n)&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;мқҙлӢӨ.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;bfs-breadth-first-search&quot;&gt;BFS: Breadth-First Search&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
